# @wardnet packages (ui, styles) are published to GitHub Packages.
# Auth token comes from the environment — NEVER commit a token.
#   Local: `gh auth refresh -s read:packages` then `export NODE_AUTH_TOKEN="$(gh auth token)"`.
#   CI:    the workflow exports the built-in GITHUB_TOKEN (packages: read).
@wardnet:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${NODE_AUTH_TOKEN}
